                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-74-off404 t18301028-74-crimeloc407"></join>. The prisoner has been in my employ since the 23rd of August - he was my <rs id="t18301028-74-deflabel408" type="occupation">warehouseman and clerk</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-74-defend667 t18301028-74-deflabel408"></join>; he had the care of my books and goods - I had reason to suspect him, and on the 12th of October, at eight o'clock at night, he left me, without giving any notice - I went to several pawnbrokers, and found my property; he did not come home to sleep on the 12th, and on the 13th I took him into custody.</p>
